platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It’s just gorgeous. The moment we began playing Dust, we couldn’t stop marveling at the beauty of its hand-painted landscapes. That first impression never fades as the action kicks in, sending you on a whirlwind adventure to uncover the truth behind the main character’s past. This 2D side-scroller blends platforming with furious combat as you bound through the air, stringing together combo after combo. Incredibly responsive controls make Dust a real pleasure to play, and we never tired of pushing ahead to see what the dazzling visuals and challenging combat had in store for us next.
